                                                        Vedantu breaks away from a typical classroom teaching structure and uses technology and customisation to enable students to interact with their chosen teacher Live Online!
                                                        In India, students often feel too shy to clarify their doubts in a crowded coaching classes. Many students travel long hours to get to class. Vedantu breaks these shackles by liberating learning and teaching from the limits of location.
                                                        Teachers that Vedantu provide include IIT grads, PhD holders and Ivy Leaguers. Parents prefer benefits of personalised teaching as it's safer and convenient.
                                                        Students are given full freedom to choose their teacher as per their convenient time. They can select any teacher irrespective of their geographical location, from the comfort of their home
                                                        Very few teams in India have a great sense for the education sector as well as how technology can be used for effective scaling, Vedantu is one such team
                                                        Vedantu uses in house technology keeping in mind potential bandwidth problems. Their technology can be used in places where the bandwidth drops to as low as 256kbps!
                                                        Traditionally, students rely on brick-and-mortar coaching centers, but companies like Vedantu are springing up and more students are supplementing offline courses with online tutoring.
